    # #2145 Next — gate implementation pending. Flag as open work.

chorus:practice-andon-state
    chorus:hasSkill chorus:skill-pull .
    # role-state declaration lives inside /pull's step 6; no standalone skill.

# chorus:practice-idle-awareness — process-only; no skill or gate. Role discipline.
# chorus:practice-signal-not-narrate — process-only; trained via feedback.
# chorus:practice-wall-clock-refresh — process-only; every-response ritual per CLAUDE.md.

